    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这本充满了亚娃星独特景观及其居民形象的数字艺术设定集，让您可以尽情领略游戏的出色美术。与此同时，Adrian Berenguer 创作的曲目（格式：MP3、WAV、FLAC）也能让您聆听到最温暖人心的声音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该艺术同捆包还包括一系列超酷壁纸。此外，还有一个独特的喀拉什（它可是亚娃星最可爱的居民之一）图纸，让您可以通过 3D 打印，将亚娃的生灵从屏幕中带进现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064170/extras/3788983c17b696996f11192d6f6508ee.poster.avif?t=1733411808\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064170/extras/3788983c17b696996f11192d6f6508ee.webm?t=1733411808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
